{
  "texts": [
    "To address the data heterogeneity problem in FL, FedMix [80] allows each client to utilize MoE to adaptive select which client expert models are relevant to it.",
    "Fed-MoEs [81] obtain all client local models pre-trained on local data.",
    "These pre-trained models, the aggregated global model, andHomo.",
    "Feature Extractor Hetero.",
    "Feature Extractor Gating Network Header Homo."
  ]
}